Assertion: to validate the test script we use Assertions.
1)hard assert
2)soft assert

Hard assert:
1)static method
2)complex TS
3)when ever your TS fail it will through the error at same line & stop execution
AssertEqual();

Soft assert:
1)non static method
2)simple TS
3)when ever your TS fail it will execute the next line code & through the error at last 
4)AssertAll();
SoftAssert sa=new SoftAssert();
sa.AssertEquals();
sa.AssertAll();

Methods:
1)AssertEquals("EC","AC");
2)AssertNotEquals("EC","AC");
3)AssertTrue(true);
4)AssertFalse(false);